## md2pdf

Convert markdown files to pdf.
Formatting manuscript following a given style is a pain.
This `R package` allow you to automatically generate publisher like documents with the minumum effort.
Therefore, researchers can focus on thinking and writing in `markdown`.

## Installation & Usage

```
#install.packages(devtools)
devtools::install_github("yangjl/md2pdf")
library(md2pdf)
```

